========================
STUDENT VALIDATION RULES
========================

1. Student Name Validation

Rule Name:
Student_Name_Validation

Formula:
ISBLANK(Name)

Error Message:
Student Name cannot be blank.



2. Roll Number Validation

Rule Name:
RollNo_Validation

Formula:
RollNo__c <= 0

Error Message:
Roll Number must be greater than 0.



3. Marks Validation

Rule Name:
Marks_Validation

Formula:
OR(
    Marks__c < 0,
    Marks__c > 100
)

Error Message:
Marks should be between 0 and 100.



4. Email Validation

No Validation Rule Required

Reason:
Salesforce automatically validates Email field format because datatype is Email.



========================
FACULTY VALIDATION RULES
========================

1. Faculty Name Validation

Rule Name:
Faculty_Name_Validation

Formula:
LEN(Name) < 3

Error Message:
Faculty Name must contain at least 3 characters.



2. Faculty ID Validation

Rule Name:
Faculty_ID_Validation

Formula:
FacultyId__c <= 0

Error Message:
Faculty ID must be greater than 0.

Note:
Keep FacultyId__c field as UNIQUE while creating field.



3. Salary Validation

Rule Name:
Salary_Validation

Formula:
OR(
    Salary__c <= 10000,
    Salary__c >= 500000
)

Error Message:
Salary must be between 10,000 and 500,000.



4. Department Validation

Rule Name:
Department_Validation

Formula:
ISBLANK(TEXT(Dept__c))

Error Message:
Please select Department.



5. Joining Date Validation

Rule Name:
JoiningDate_Validation

Formula:
JoiningDate__c > TODAY()

Error Message:
Joining Date cannot be a future date.